## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Performance Optimization & Latency Reduction (Area 1)

#### [MODIFY] [app.py](file:///d:/Projects/Sand-Mining_Detection/src/dashboard/app.py)
* **SQLite Transaction Batching:** Refactor the simulated telemetry log insertion logic. Instead of executing database insert and commit statements directly at 3 Hz, append telemetry logs to a thread-safe in-memory buffer (`telemetry_buffer = []`).
* **Asynchronous Flusher:** Implement an async background task `_flush_telemetry_db_loop` that runs every 5 seconds to bulk-insert buffered telemetry records and commit them in a single transaction.
* **Clustering Throttle:** Decouple `ClusterEngine.cluster_detections` from the high-frequency 3 Hz telemetry loop. Run it as an independent async task every 3 seconds to keep CPU cycles cool.
* **YOLO Image Size Auto-throttling:** Automatically set `imgsz=640` for normal altitudes and reserve `imgsz=1280` only during active high-altitude flights.

---

### Component 2: Advanced Spatial Analytics & Small Object Detection (Area 3)

#### [NEW] [sahi_detector.py](file:///d:/Projects/Sand-Mining_Detection/src/detection/sahi_detector.py)
* **Implement Slicing Logics:** Create a utility that slices a high-resolution input frame (e.g., `1920x1080`) into overlapping slices (e.g., `640x640` with `20%` overlap).
* **Patch Inference & Merge:** Execute YOLO on each slice independently, then shift the bounding box coordinates back to the global frame. Merge overlapping boxes using Non-Maximum Suppression (NMS) or Intersection-over-Union (IoU) criteria to resolve redundant detections.
* **Gated Execution:** Enable SAHI dynamically based on drone altitude inputs.

#### [MODIFY] [gps_projector.py](file:///d:/Projects/Sand-Mining_Detection/src/detection/gps_projector.py)
* **Terrain & Elevation Corrections:** Add terrain elevation parameter offsets to the projection mathematical formulas to adjust coordinate projections based on land contour elevation differences.

